    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enter a realm cracked in two...</h2>... divided between reality and memories, its shattered fragments leaving windows between worlds. Those with the power to move between them will face shadowy monsters, solve devious puzzles, and win new abilities. Confront the memory, and reforge the fragments of the past into a shining new destiny.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115160/extras/b1ee327097c8ef47fa1fb1a43cc346a3.poster.avif?t=1660842219\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115160/extras/b1ee327097c8ef47fa1fb1a43cc346a3.webm?t=1660842219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115160/extras/b1ee327097c8ef47fa1fb1a43cc346a3.mp4?t=1660842219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Walk Between Worlds:</strong> Use your magical powers to cross the border between reality and memory.<br></li><li> <strong>The Fragments:</strong> Shattered windows that allow passage and spread their influence.<br></li><li> <strong>The Wretched:</strong> Shadowy enemies that will stalk you through the realms.<br></li><li> <strong>Atmospheric Levels:</strong> A combination of platforming under pressure, unique enemies and melancholy ambience.<br></li><li> <strong>Reality-Bending Abilities:</strong> Opening new paths and possibilities, letting you change the world itself.<br></li><li> <strong>Fluid Beauty:</strong> A world drawn and animated by hand, rich in detail when still and in motion.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115160/extras/44b0ce951b3b68d55d2d681d606b2a70.pos